SUMMARY:Advanced Ride (B) LV Lapps Farm (38R)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\n***Be Safe\, Have Fun\, a
 nd Ride Together***\n\nRide leader: Matt Pammer\nAnticipated Average Pace:
  16-18 mph\nRoute: [https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/lv-lapps-farm
 -ice-cream-ride-37r/](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/lv-lapps-fa
 rm-ice-cream-ride-37r/)\n\nThis is a B level ride. The ride leader will ri
 de at the advertised average speed. This is intended to be a group ride wi
 th a no-drop rule as the main goal. The ride leader will do his/her best t
 o keep the group together with occasional regroupings and a sweeper may al
 so be appointed at the start.\nPlease do not join this ride if you are not
  willing to ride with the group. If you exceed the posted pace\, you will 
 be riding by yourself and encouraged to join a faster group. If maintainin
 g a 16-18 mph average is beyond your current ability level\, please consid
 er joining a slower ride first.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Plea
 se bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2
  inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we req
 uire LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride. Being on
  Meetup does not mean you are a club member.\nJoin here [Member Signup](ht
 tps://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148)\nY
 our RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's Code of Conduct: [Code o
 f Conduct](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_
 id=257148)\nGuidance if an incident occurs: [Incident Actions](https://lan
 casterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=326137
 )
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3140532
 94/
