SUMMARY:Watch Party of the Paris-Roubaix Monument Classic
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nCome join us (free admiss
 ion) for a Paris-Roubaix Watch Party hosted by The Common Wheel and Lancas
 ter Bike Club! This is the only Monument classic race that Tadej Pogacar h
 as not yet won and he will be going full guns to bag this palmare. Lots of
  coffee and donuts will be served (no charge) and it should be a great tim
 e had by all! Note that the event will take place at the E King St (Reserv
 oir Park) location of The Common Wheel. Kindly click the attend button so 
 we know you’re coming. See you soon!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3141728
